These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
House: palace, gothic-revival, cottage, modern, colonial
There 5 different types of food: banana, artichoke, pear, corn, asparagus
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, disco, funk, d&b, country
There are 5 different favourite colors: pink, chestnut, mauve, green, blood-red
 1. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 2. the person eating pear is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 3. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 4. the cottage house is the cottage house##1
 5. the person who likes pink is the person eating banana##1
 6. the colonial house is on the left of the cottage house##1
 7. the fan dubstep is on the left of the fan funk##1
 8. the modern house is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 9. the modern house is on the far right##1
10. the palace house is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
11. the colonial house is between the fan disco and the person eating asparagus##2
12. the fan d&b is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
13. the fan country is on the right of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| House      | palace        | gothic-revival | colonial     | cottage   | modern |
| Food   | pear     | artichoke      | corn | asparagus   | banana    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | disco     | dubstep | funk | country  |
| Color           | chestnut | mauve      | blood-red     | green   | pink     |

