.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, cola, mirinda, hot-chocolate
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daffodil, iris, marigold, rose, dahlia
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, bridge, whist, poker
House: palace, cottage, art-deco, ranch-style, townhouse
 1. the townhouse house is in the middle##1
 2. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 5. the cottage house is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person who growsdahlia##2
 6. the ranch-style house is the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the palace house##1
 8. the person playing bridge is the person who growsrose##1
 9. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
11. the person playing bridge is the person drinking cola##1
12. the cottage house is on the right of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Beverage         | mirinda | almond-milk | hot-chocolate    | coffee  | cola    |
| Flower   | dahlia    | iris       | marigold      | daffodil | rose        |
| Game   | poker   | canasta     | mah-jongg    | whist  | bridge     |
| House     | art-deco    | cottage | townhouse | ranch-style | palace |

