 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
10. the person playing snooker is the person drinking fanta##1
11. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
12. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
13. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person drinking soy-milk and the fonseca-smoker##2

