The people have 5 different jobs:  lawyer, nurse, designer, entrepreneur, project-manager
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, montecristo, fonseca, havana, bongani
 1. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the nurse##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 4. the bongani-smoker is between the entrepreneur and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the project-manager is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is the nurse##1
 9. the project-manager is in the middle##1
10. the entrepreneur is the oliveros-smoker##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
12. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the designer##1
13. the nurse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
