5 different games are played: chess, domino, whist, go, snooker
5 different pets are kept: snake, hamster, chinchilla, bird, fish
 1. the person playing snooker is between the owner of the hamster and the person playing domino##2
 2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing go##1
 3. the malaysian is the person eating pineapple##1
 4. the colombian is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the malaysian##1
 6. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 8. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the malaysian##1
 9. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
10. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person playing whist and the person eating lettuce##2
12. the australian is on the right of the person eating peach##1
13. the canadian is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Nationality    | canadian       | australian    | dutch | malaysian  | colombian        |
| Food       | peach | eggplant | lettuce  | pineapple | corn    |
| Game       | whist        | go   | domino  | snooker   | chess |
| Pet   | bird       | chinchilla      | fish      | snake | hamster  |

