.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different nationalities: nigerian, british, japanese, american, thai
The people have 5 different hobbies: magic-tricks, drawing, dancing, fishing, video-games
There 5 different types of food: orange, eggplant, peach, papaya, spinach
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, scooter, bike, bus, taxi
 1. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person eating peach and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
 3. the american is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 4. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the person eating orange is in the middle##1
 6. the american is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person driving the scooter##2
 7. the person driving the bus is the japanese##1
 8. the nigerian is the person driving the bike##1
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person eating peach##1
11. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person eating eggplant##1
12. the person eating papaya is on the far left##1
13. the thai is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Nationality      | nigerian      | british         | american      | japanese | thai     |
| Hobby           | drawing | dancing | fishing | video-games    | magic-tricks  |
| Food   | papaya  | eggplant    | orange | peach    | spinach |
| Transport   | bike  | scooter        | jet-ski   | bus    | taxi     |

