.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, climbing, soccer, skiing, cycling
House: modern, ranch-style, gothic-revival, futuristic, craftsman
There are 5 different favourite colors: pink, lavender, brown, blue, ebony
The people have 5 different jobs:  journalist, scientist, bartender, firefighter, analyst
 1. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the scientist##1
 2. the futuristic house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the analyst##1
 4. the bartender is on the far left##1
 5. the person who likes lavender is between the modern house and the person who likes pink##2
 6. the modern house is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is between the journalist and the person who's sport is cycling##2
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is swimming##2
 9. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
10. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Sport         | cycling  | soccer | skiing   | climbing      | swimming |
| House   | modern   | futuristic    | ranch-style | craftsman | gothic-revival      |
| Color           | brown | lavender    | pink       | blue     | ebony      |
| Job     | bartender | analyst        | journalist  | scientist        | firefighter    |

