.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: amber, ivory, yellow, blue, red
5 different games are played: chess, go, bridge, billiard, monopoly
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: ice-hockey, cycling, sailing, handball, water-polo
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, january, august, december, september
 1. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
 3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 4. the person playing monopoly is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's sport is sailing##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 7. the person playing bridge is the person who's sport is handball##1
 8. the person who likes blue is the person who's sport is cycling##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's sport is cycling##1
10. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
12. the person playing go is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Color         | yellow    | red  | ivory  | amber      | blue |
| Game   | go    | monopoly   | billiard | bridge | chess   |
| Sport   | sailing | ice-hockey    | water-polo    | handball       | cycling         |
| Birthday   | december  | january | september    | august     | july      |

 